<Window
    x:Class="BF1GamePatch.MainWindow"
    xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
    xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
    xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
    xmlns:local="clr-namespace:BF1GamePatch"
    xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
    x:Name="Window_Main"
    Title="战地1游戏文件降级工具（使用电影工具专用）"
    Width="700"
    Height="500"
    Closing="Window_Main_Closing"
    Icon="/Assets/Icons/Favicon.ico"
    Loaded="Window_Main_Loaded"
    ResizeMode="CanMinimize"
    WindowStartupLocation="CenterScreen"
    mc:Ignorable="d">

    <Grid>
        <Grid.RowDefinitions>
            <RowDefinition Height="Auto" />
            <RowDefinition />
            <RowDefinition Height="Auto" />
        </Grid.RowDefinitions>

        <StackPanel Grid.Row="0">
            <TextBlock
                Margin="10,5,5,0"
                FontSize="14"
                FontWeight="Bold">
                1. 单独复制一份战地1正版最新版本游戏文件到任意文件夹（游戏大概80g左右）
            </TextBlock>
            <TextBlock
                Margin="10,5,5,0"
                FontSize="14"
                FontWeight="Bold">
                2. 点击下面按钮，然后选择上面复制的战地1文件夹中"bf1.exe"即可，程序会自动开始降级操作
            </TextBlock>
            <Button
                x:Name="Button_RunGamePatch"
                Grid.Row="2"
                Margin="5,5,5,0"
                Padding="10"
                Click="Button_RunGamePatch_Click"
                Content="开始战地1游戏文件降级"
                IsEnabled="False" />
        </StackPanel>

        <TextBox
            x:Name="TextBox_Logger"
            Grid.Row="1"
            Margin="5"
            Padding="7"
            Cursor="Arrow"
            HorizontalScrollBarVisibility="Auto"
            IsReadOnly="True"
            TextWrapping="NoWrap"
            VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Auto" />
    </Grid>

</Window>
